## UI & Backend polish — TODO.md batch

**Context:** Applied all items from `releasereq/TODO.md` — UI cleanup, Graph DB
card improvements, Cockpit parity, schedule de-duplication, and Health check
coverage.

### Changes

1. **DT / Knowledge Graph — remove Entity Type dropdown** (`src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_sigmagraph.html`)
   - Removed the redundant "Entity Type" label + select from the Filter tab.
     Entity type visibility is still controlled via the View → Entity Types chips.
   - `src/front/static/query/js/query-sigmagraph.js` — already uses null-guards,
     no JS update required.

2. **Domain / Build — Graph DB (Lakebase) card** (`src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_sync.html`, `src/front/static/query/js/query-sync.js`, `src/back/objects/digitaltwin/DigitalTwin.py`)
   - Removed the long `graphEngineFootnoteLakebase` footnote below the card.
